    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the bacon is in the oven, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Squeeze the juice of the<strong> grated ginger</strong> into a small bowl</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1674558492903-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1674558492903-x400.jpg",
