            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>rested</strong> <strong>pancake batter</strong> from the fridge and add the <strong>grated garlic</strong>, <strong>grated ginger</strong> and 2/3 of the <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>okonomiyaki pancake mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1674558502820-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1674558502820-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1674558502820-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1674558502820-x1000.jpg",
