            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1674558516801-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pancake[s] are cooking, shred your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely, lengthways</p><p>Combine <strong>half</strong> your <strong>honey</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) with your <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>and a small pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your<strong> cheats okonomiyaki sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1674558525778-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1674558525778-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1674558525778-x700.jpg",
