            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1674558543713-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1674558543713-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1674558543713-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1674558543713-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Japanese-style okonomiyaki pancake slices</strong> stacked, then top with the <strong>candied bacon</strong> and the <strong>gingery</strong> <strong>slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle your<strong> mayo </strong>and <strong>cheats okonomiyaki sauce </strong>all over</p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> shimichi togarashi </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
